troductory text is added to read as follows: §245.1 Eligibility. * * * * * (c) Ineligible aliens. The following categories of aliens are ineligible to apply for adjustment of status to that of a lawful permanent resident alien under section 245 of the Act: * * * * * 12. In §245.1, paragraphs (b)(7) through (b)(10) are redesignated as paragraphs (c)(1) through (c)(4) respectively; and paragraphs (b)(12) through (b)(14) are redesignated as paragraphs (c)(5) through (c)(7) respectively. 13. In §245.1, paragraph (b)(11) is redesignated as paragraph (b)(7) and paragraph (b)(15) is redesignated as paragraph (b)(8). 14. In §245.1, the second sentence of the newly redesignated paragraph (g) is amended by revising the phrase ``Department of State Visa Office Bulletin on Availability of Immigrant Visa Numbers'' to read: ``Department of State Bureau of Consular Affairs Visa Bulletin''. 15. In §245.1, the third sentence of the newly redesignated paragraph (g) is amended by revising the phrase ``not later than'' to read: ``earlier than''.
